{"tid":253851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有學六壬或者茅山嘅巴打入","createTime":"2017-05-22T17:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T03:55:20.000Z","uid":37855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"523dcb9359fbe37055a53c575be37bf0630cc274","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"見連登好少相關post，想同各位有學嘅巴絲討論下<br />\n小弟學左六壬一年左右，而我老豆都有學，而且係師傅，自細都聽過唔少故仔，可惜幾年前走左。<br />\n我係自己有興趣下同埋想將屋企個神壇接手嘅情況下走左去學，都只係見識過同聽過少少野。<br />\n有冇巴絲可以一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a1a4ca0422058bc61e635596a8d41811213e15","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f8e68fb77ee91ab9a7b4092787ae17c55803e90","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d0ddfb0d5ca3d88bf1d1b0af08c1d583a1b0f9","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"唔好沉呀"},{"pid":"d76602b4279b2fddd068bbd65bd279c4a9cda1a5","tid":253851,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:26:50.000Z","msg":"跟邊個師傅，係咪有分上下茅，覺得出面好多神棍，跟錯人學哂時間"},{"pid":"a516ef513926bfbb1415514b590f8fa12b4c711d","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟邊個師傅，係咪有分上下茅，覺得出面好多神棍，跟錯人學哂時間</blockquote><br />\n有分上下茅嫁，奇實神棍都真係多，但有啲其實都唔可以話係神棍，只係學藝未精，但又想幫人或者認叻咁，最後咪都做唔到"},{"pid":"839e8b54a8b92193c39e8c441e3db037853163ce","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟邊個師傅，係咪有分上下茅，覺得出面好多神棍，跟錯人學哂時間</blockquote><br />\n有分上下茅嫁，奇實神棍都真係多，但有啲其實都唔可以話係神棍，只係學藝未精，但又想幫人或者認叻咁，最後咪都做唔到</blockquote><br />\n好多人都覺得六壬茅山哩啲係邪法之類，其實我覺得都係幫人，就冇分。而以我所知上茅下茅係行緊唔同方面，上茅係行緊神嗰面，而下茅就行鬼嗰面。當然我對於茅山方面都唔太清楚，有茅山巴打見到有錯請屌"},{"pid":"1988d58853e10464df75b7d6080f677d541b27db","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"上網見到比人劈嗰啲係真嫁，我試過，第一次嗰陣真係驚到腳震，但又真係好神奇地冇事，只係痛同紅左，把刀真係利嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d074eedc972427ca337ba9c018e0029c36e10aec","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3991b14606e7c3e242f2dfd8238aa153b33eb8e2","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cb0361779a6cefaeb0c3e86928c0646d62d7e784","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1</blockquote><br />\n2"},{"pid":"6cc36b833fce5ca9feabd99b23e4b896a4553a91","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1</blockquote><br />\n2</blockquote><br />\n3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bb938f9c97617bc6d4ffd81d83ce9be074ba20","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1</blockquote><br />\n2</blockquote><br />\n3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4"},{"pid":"7c5627d3bd0392ebced7cb4ea2d63fa4ba24e437","tid":253851,"uid":37855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1</blockquote><br />\n2</blockquote><br />\n3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj